    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CardGuid], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0], [c0].[StateId] AS [StateId0]

) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CardGuid], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0], [c0].[StateId] AS [StateId0]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Address], [t].[CardGuid], [t].[CityId], [t].[CityName], [t].[CommunityId], [t].[CommunityName], [t].[CommunityTypeId], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[FeesMonthly], [t].[GracePeriod], [t].[NoOfParkingLot], [t].[NoOfUnits], [t].[PICEmail], [t].[PICMobile], [t].[PICName], [t].[StateId], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Id0], [t].[Name], [t].[Id1], [t].[Name0], [t].[StateId0], [v].[Id], [v].[Amount], [v].[ChargeTypeId], [v].[CommunityId], [v].[CreatedBy], [v].[CreatedDate], [v].[NoOfVistorParkingLot], [v].[Status], [v].[UpdatedBy], [v].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CardGuid], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0], [c0].[StateId] AS [StateId0]
    FROM [Community] AS [c]

) AS [t]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-03-22 12:00:54.977 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (44ms) [Parameters=[@__roleId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-03-22 12:41:21.926 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (33ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]
    WHERE [m0].[Id] = [r].[SubMenuId]) AS [SubMenuName], [m].[Name] AS [MenuName], [r0].[Name] AS [RoleName]
FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]
